===============
  Fingertier
===============

Fingertier (German for the Aye-eye) is a minimalistic finger friendly music player for mobile devices. It is optimised for smart phones with small touch screens, like the OpenMoko Freerunner.

Dependencies:
 * Vala
 * GTK+2.0
 * Gstreamer

Build: 
 type 'make'

Run:
 type 'make test'



GTK layout:

+------------------------+
|                        |
|       cover image      |
|                        |
+------------------------+
|         artist         |
|         title          |
|         album          |
+------------------------+
|         3/120          |
+------------------------+
| prev, play/pause, next |
+------------------------+
